06:16.529 --> 06:18.163
<i>Daphne: Hey, Sharee, wait up.</i>

06:20.366 --> 06:22.534
Hey, is everything okay?

06:22.568 --> 06:24.302
You weren't in school last week.

06:24.336 --> 06:25.470
Yeah, because I was being interviewed

06:25.504 --> 06:27.138
by child protective services.

06:27.173 --> 06:29.374
They came to the house.
Oh, and my mom thinks

06:29.408 --> 06:32.143
our neighbor was the one who
called, but I know it was you.

06:32.178 --> 06:33.244
I was worried.

06:33.279 --> 06:35.213
You said yourself she's sick.

06:35.247 --> 06:37.182
I also said I could handle it.

06:37.216 --> 06:38.550
You're lucky they came when
she was having a good day.

06:38.644 --> 06:40.578
Wait, that's it? They're
not gonna do anything?

06:40.613 --> 06:43.448
Actually, yeah. They're
gonna do surprise visits.

06:43.482 --> 06:45.617
So I have that to look forward to.

06:45.651 --> 06:47.585
You promised you wouldn't say anything.

06:47.620 --> 06:49.587
I know. And I'm sorry.

06:49.622 --> 06:51.256
But I didn't know what else to do.

06:51.290 --> 06:52.624
I was just trying to be a good friend.

06:52.658 --> 06:55.293
Ugh. Right. There's not
enough drama in your own life,

06:55.361 --> 06:56.361
so you had to meddle in mine.

06:56.395 --> 06:58.429
No, that's not it at all.

06:58.464 --> 07:00.398
Look...

07:00.432 --> 07:02.133
my mom's a recovering alcoholic,

07:02.167 --> 07:03.434
so I know what it's like.

07:03.469 --> 07:07.171
You're scared that if anybody
finds out what's going on,

07:07.206 --> 07:08.439
you might never get her back,

07:08.474 --> 07:11.175
so you keep lying to yourself,
hoping it'll get better.

07:11.644 --> 07:13.511
But it doesn't.

07:13.546 --> 07:16.347
So far, the only person
who's lied to me is you.

07:16.382 --> 07:18.249
