They're for a meeting
Wes is hosting tomorrow

07:33.666 --> 07:35.633
for "The friends of East Riverside."

07:35.668 --> 07:37.535
He wants to get some
buy-in from the community

07:37.570 --> 07:39.203
before we break ground on the project.

07:39.238 --> 07:41.606
Oh, I had no idea that
it was going to be so big.

07:41.640 --> 07:43.608
I mean, a whole city block?

07:43.642 --> 07:45.443
That's Wes. His motto...

07:45.477 --> 07:47.579
"Think big, then think bigger."

07:47.643 --> 07:49.510
And what about those businesses

07:49.545 --> 07:50.678
in the building you're tearing down?

07:50.713 --> 07:52.280
I mean, some of them have been there

07:52.314 --> 07:53.414
since before you were born.

07:53.449 --> 07:56.250
Wes will take care of them.

07:56.285 --> 07:58.286
Trust me, Mario can buy three pizza places

07:58.320 --> 08:00.388
and Hector never has to cut hair again.

08:00.422 --> 08:02.390
Oh, well. Good for Hector and Mario.

08:02.424 --> 08:03.558
No no no, not just them.

08:03.592 --> 08:06.327
This is gonna be good for
the whole neighborhood.

08:06.362 --> 08:07.395
I'll see you later.

08:09.870 --> 08:11.605
_

08:11.608 --> 08:14.335
Yeah, I am totally billing my dad

08:14.370 --> 08:17.572
for whatever amount of therapy it
takes to erase that image from my brain.

08:17.573 --> 08:19.486
_

08:19.508 --> 08:20.642
She doesn't know yet.

08:20.676 --> 08:24.612
I mean this in the nicest way possible.

08:24.647 --> 08:26.180
She would totally freak out.

08:26.215 --> 08:28.483
I'm pretty sure it's gonna blow over.

08:28.517 --> 08:32.587
My mom's not gonna throw
away 20 years of marriage

08:32.621 --> 08:34.355
because of one kiss, right?

08:36.900 --> 08:39.129
_

08:41.397 --> 08:43.563
Now tell me what you really think.

08:46.572 --> 08:52.019
_

08:52.820 --> 08:56.843
_

08:57.312 --> 08:58.579
You never told me that.

08:59.580 --> 09:03.011
_

09:03.012 --> 09:07.335
