17:02.922 --> 17:04.189
- Really?
- Mm-hmm.

17:04.223 --> 17:05.190
Wow.

17:13.165 --> 17:14.999
This is so cool.

17:15.034 --> 17:17.769
How do you not eavesdrop all the time?

17:17.803 --> 17:20.003
It's like having a super power.

17:23.175 --> 17:24.209
What's that?

17:24.242 --> 17:26.176
Oh, no. That's nothing.

17:27.230 --> 17:28.299
