20:15.114 --> 20:17.215
I know, but I thought of that.

20:17.249 --> 20:19.150
We give out free flu shots at the clinic,

20:19.184 --> 20:21.019
so what if you tell her you're
worried about getting sick

20:21.053 --> 20:22.820
and ask her to bring you in?

20:22.855 --> 20:24.889
What happens when she finds
out why she's really there?

20:24.924 --> 20:26.224
The psychologist will know what to do,

20:26.258 --> 20:28.026
but at least we'll get her diagnosed.

20:28.060 --> 20:29.193
That's the first step.

20:29.228 --> 20:32.130
(Sighs)

20:32.164 --> 20:33.264
Okay.

20:34.900 --> 20:36.134
Let's do it.

20:44.944 --> 20:46.044
You got everything?

20:46.078 --> 20:48.813
Or you need some help
carrying in your soap box?

20:48.847 --> 20:52.150
I should have talked to you
before coming to that meeting.

20:52.184 --> 20:54.052
Yeah, you should have.

20:54.086 --> 20:56.187
What were you thinking?

20:56.221 --> 20:58.189
I was thinking about our neighborhood.

20:58.223 --> 20:59.223
Really?

20:59.258 --> 21:01.759
You haven't lived there in two years.

21:01.794 --> 21:03.761
And in case your memory's a little foggy,

21:03.796 --> 21:05.763
East Riverside was never
that great to begin with.

21:05.798 --> 21:08.199
We still have friends there and family.

21:08.233 --> 21:09.801
I'm looking out for them.

21:09.835 --> 21:12.003
And what exactly am I doing?

21:12.037 --> 21:14.172
(Sighs)

21:14.206 --> 21:16.074
You're looking out for your business.

21:16.108 --> 21:18.076
Okay.

21:18.110 --> 21:19.177
Fine.

21:19.211 --> 21:20.244
But I'm also trying to make

21:20.279 --> 21:22.080
east riverside a better place to live.

21:22.114 --> 21:23.114
What is wrong with that?

21:23.148 --> 21:25.783
I came to that meeting

21:25.818 --> 21:27.151
to listen with an open mind.

21:27.186 --> 21:29.087
I figured that maybe I was wrong.

21:29.121 --> 21:32.156
And then I saw that developer guy

21:32.191 --> 21:35.793
trot you out like his prized bull.

21:35.828 --> 21:37.161
(Sighs deeply) Is that what this is about?

21:37.196 --> 21:39.197
He needs a latina on his side.

21:39.231 --> 21:41.799
He's using you for the color of your skin.

21:41.834 --> 21:42.934
That is ridiculous.

21:42.968 --> 21:46.004
Wes hired me for my design ability

21:46.038 --> 21:48.806
before he even heard of East Riverside.

21:48.841 --> 21:52.243
I can't believe you. I am finally about
to get something good going for myself.

21:52.277 --> 21:53.811
Why do you have to take me down?

21:53.846 --> 21:54.846
That's not what I'm doing.

21:54.880 --> 21:56.848
Ah...

21:58.183 --> 21:59.150
I need this.

21:59.184 --> 22:01.753
And I expect you to get on board.

22:01.787 --> 22:02.954
<i>¿Me entiendes?</i>

22:11.864 --> 22:14.198
Sharee just texted me.
They're on their way in.

22:14.233 --> 22:16.200
Dr. Edwards is running a little late.

22:16.235 --> 22:17.235
Will they be able to wait?

22:17.269 --> 22:19.137
I don't know.

22:19.171 --> 22:21.139
Sharee's mom thinks
they're here for a flu shot.

22:21.173 --> 22:23.808
She doesn't know she's
meeting a psychologist?

22:24.943 --> 22:26.044
We didn't think she'd come.

22:27.880 --> 22:30.782
Oh, there she is.

22:30.816 --> 22:32.984
That was nice of you to set this up.

22:33.018 --> 22:35.920
I can't have my girl getting sick.

22:35.954 --> 22:38.823
Ms. Gifford, Sharee, this is Dr. Jackson.

22:38.857 --> 22:40.024
Hi, there.

22:40.059 --> 22:41.092
Hi.

22:41.126 --> 22:43.094
Well, let's get my baby this flu shot.

22:45.264 --> 22:47.065
Um, Ms. Gifford,

22:47.099 --> 22:48.933
<i>why don't you step into my office?</i>

22:48.967 --> 22:50.902
There's a few forms we need to fill out.

22:52.037 --> 22:54.005
Oh. Okay.

23:01.246 --> 23:03.815
<i>(Ragtime music playing)</i>

23:03.849 --> 23:05.983
(Patrons chattering)

23:06.018 --> 23:07.819
John: When you said guys'
night, I thought you meant like

23:07.853 --> 23:10.088
a sports bar or something. (Chuckles)

23:10.122 --> 23:12.824
We haven't been here in, like, forever.

23:12.858 --> 23:15.760
Is this really what you wanna do?

23:15.794 --> 23:17.829
Heck yeah. I love this place.

23:17.863 --> 23:19.797
They got everything... skee ball,

23:19.832 --> 23:21.032
air hockey, go-carts.

23:21.066 --> 23:22.033
Mm.

23:24.069 --> 23:25.837
Your mom and Bay.

23:25.871 --> 23:27.038
Surprise!

23:27.072 --> 23:28.039
Family night!

23:28.073 --> 23:29.774
(Sighs deeply)

23:36.010 --> 23:39.078
So, how are things going at Toby's?

23:39.393 --> 23:41.627
Oh, we're having a blast.

23:41.662 --> 23:44.363
Grilling a lot of exotic meats.

23:44.398 --> 23:47.400
I've been getting a lot of writing done.

23:47.434 --> 23:49.302
Oh, that's fantastic.

23:49.336 --> 23:50.536
Should have kicked me out years ago.

23:50.571 --> 23:52.605
We were just talking about

23:52.639 --> 23:54.574
all the great memories that we've had here.

23:54.693 --> 23:56.360
My seventh birthday.

23:56.395 --> 23:59.296
The night my little league
team won the championship.

23:59.331 --> 24:01.699
But you know what my
all-time favorite memory is?

24:01.733 --> 24:05.369
The time the four of us
conquered "the pig's trough."

24:05.404 --> 24:06.637
- Uh...
- That's very sweet of you two...

24:06.672 --> 24:08.673
<i>- (bell clanging)
- Here you go.</i>

24:08.707 --> 24:10.675
One pig's trough.

24:10.709 --> 24:12.343
<i>You guys know the rules.</i>

24:12.377 --> 24:13.477
You've got 15 minutes.

24:13.512 --> 24:14.645
<i>If you clean the trough</i>

24:14.680 --> 24:16.313
<i>like good little piggies,</i>

24:16.348 --> 24:17.415
<i>we put your picture up on the wall.</i>

24:17.449 --> 24:18.416
<i>Ready,</i>

24:18.450 --> 24:19.550
set,

24:19.584 --> 24:21.285
go.

24:21.319 --> 24:22.720
Well, let's go. Time's a-wastin'.

24:22.754 --> 24:24.622
- Come on.
- You're kidding, right?

24:24.656 --> 24:25.723
<i>- No way.
- Hey, we've done it before.</i>

24:25.757 --> 24:27.258
10 years ago.

24:27.292 --> 24:28.426
You know I gotta go easy on this

24:28.460 --> 24:30.294
- since the heart attack.
- Suck it up!

24:30.328 --> 24:31.429
We are the Kennishes.

24:31.463 --> 24:32.697
There is no challenge that we can't face.

24:32.731 --> 24:34.398
(Ticking)

24:34.433 --> 24:35.633
Together.

24:37.602 --> 24:39.637
<i>Mary Beth: I... I love your place.</i>

24:40.470 --> 24:42.924
_

